onsolidating brands and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1279478271/image_1279478271.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745693-toro-the-stability-investors-need-in-the-next-tariff-cycle", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:57:54", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745691", "title": "FRI: Real Estate ETF With Some Exclusions And A High Fee", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Real estate growth graph\" data-id=\"2148675525\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1063px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Rasi Bhadramani</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>FRI strategy</strong></h2> <p><strong>First Trust S&amp;P REIT Index Fund</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FRI\" title=\"First Trust S&amp;P REIT Index Fund ETF\">FRI</a></span>) was launched on 5/8/2007 and tracks the S&amp;P United States REIT Index. It has a portfolio of 136 equity REITs, a 30-day SEC yield of 3.16% and a net</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148675525/image_2148675525.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745691-fri-real-estate-etf-with-some-exclusions-and-a-high-fee", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:54:16", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745689", "title": "Investing Amid Fed Uncertainty: Where To Place Your Bets Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Department of Treasury\" data-id=\"2163652419\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Douglas Rissing</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>U.S. stocks sold off Wednesday, were neutral on Thursday, and are up quite a bit on Friday as I'm submitting final edits. A lot of realized volatility despite the fed cutting once more by the consensus 0.25bp. However, the Federal Reserve is now</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163652419/image_2163652419.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745689-investing-amid-fed-uncertainty-where-to-place-your-bets-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:49:19", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745688", "title": "iHeartMedia: An Underpriced 'Call Option'", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A home studio for recording podcasts\" data-id=\"1472176196\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Milan Markovic/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>When things go wrong at highly levered companies, the equity becomes a \u201cstub\u201d, meaning that its value is only derived by its convexity. That is, the probability that before an actual restructuring and debt equitization, things might go better than</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1472176196/image_1472176196.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745688-iheartmedia-an-underpriced-call-option", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:44:16", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745686", "title": "Lamb Weston: Another Rough Quarter, But Valuation Is Improving (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496156677/image_1496156677.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up large group of french fries background\" data-id=\"1496156677\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496156677/image_1496156677.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496156677/image_1496156677.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496156677/image_1496156677.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496156677/image_1496156677.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496156677/image_1496156677.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496156677/image_1496156677.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496156677/image_1496156677.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496156677/image_1496156677.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">imagedepotpro</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I last covered potato products maker <strong>Lamb Weston </strong>(<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LW\" title=\"Lamb Weston Holdings, Inc.\">LW</a></span>) in July. At the time, I warned that the stock <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4703433-lamb-weston-isnt-as-cheap-as-it-may-seem-lw-stock\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4703433-lamb-weston-isnt-as-cheap-as-it-may-seem-lw-stock\" target=\"_blank\">wasn't as cheap</a> as it seemed.</p> <p>It's true that Lamb Weston's P/E ratio had come down significantly and the stock seemed</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1496156677/image_1496156677.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745686-lamb-weston-another-rough-quarter-but-valuation-is-improving-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:32:49", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745685", "title": "Kaltura Improves Operating Efficiencies But Revenue Growth Lags", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Visual contents concept. Stereoscopic image. Hologram. Streaming video. NFT. Non-fungible token.\" data-id=\"1598006221\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">metamorworks</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Outlook</h2> <p><strong>Kaltura</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KLTR\" title=\"Kaltura, Inc.\">KLTR</a></span>) reported Q3 2024 <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4255279-kaltura-non-gaap-eps-of-001-beats-by-003-revenue-of-443m-beats-by-124m\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4255279-kaltura-non-gaap-eps-of-001-beats-by-003-revenue-of-443m-beats-by-124m\" target=\"_blank\">financial results</a> in early November, beating both revenue and earnings estimates followed by the stock rising sharply as a result.</p> <p>I previously wrote about KLTR in August 2023 with a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4622713-kaltura-scant-revenue-growth-2023\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4622713-kaltura-scant-revenue-growth-2023\" target=\"_blank\">Hold</a> outlook due</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1598006221/image_1598006221.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745685-kaltura-improves-operating-efficiencies-but-revenue-growth-lags", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:24:14", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745683", "title": "Micron Technology Q1: Undervalued And Innovative", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Micron Technology Inc. One of american leader in semiconductor devices, dynamic random-access memory, flash memory, USB flash drives, solid-state drives.\" data-id=\"1150565928\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5760px\" height=\"3840px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">vzphotos</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis </h2> <p><b>Micron Technology, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MU\" title=\"Micron Technology, Inc.\">MU</a></span>) reported a solid <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387691-micron-tumbles-weak-q2-forecast-fails-to-overcome-q1-results\">Q1 2025</a>, with revenue and profits hitting record levels in the three months ended November 2024. However, disappointing <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4387865-earnings-snapshot-micron-fq2-outlook-undershoots-expectations-while-fq1-tops-consensus\">Q2 2024 guidance</a> weighed down on shares. Two</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1150565928/image_1150565928.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745683-micron-technology-q1-undervalued-and-innovative", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 00:19:38", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745681", "title": "HIGH: When Options Spreads Do Not Work", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2058537479/image_2058537479.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Only 1 of 5 ladders reach in ascending order\" data-id=\"2058537479\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1122px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_